---
description: Sanmitra backend safety guardrails for all AI edits
globs:
  - "**/*"
alwaysApply: true
---

Follow repository policy in `/AGENTS.md`.

Critical rules:
- Do not use `git add .`.
- Stage explicit file paths only.
- Never commit `.env` or secrets.
- Never track `external-repos/` in this backend repo.
- Run required checks before proposing commit:
  - `python -m compileall app scripts tests`
  - `python scripts/check_text_integrity.py app scripts .github/workflows`
  - `python scripts/check_repository_safety.py`
  - `python -m pytest`
